Okay.

1221
01:06:41.564 --> 01:06:42.553
What?

1222
01:06:48.337 --> 01:06:49.497
Okay.

1223
01:06:49.739 --> 01:06:51.104
Is this what
you were expecting?

1224
01:06:51.173 --> 01:06:53.073
Because I. for one.
am flabbergasted.

1225
01:06:53.142 --> 01:06:54.234
Okay.

1226
01:06:54.310 --> 01:06:55.538
Felicia. what are you doing?

1227
01:06:55.611 --> 01:06:57.272
What's going on.
Felicia?

1228
01:06:57.346 --> 01:06:59.280
Richie found out
I was e-mailing Cathy.

1229
01:06:59.348 --> 01:07:02.112
and he came here to kill
us all. But I shot him.

1230
01:07:02.184 --> 01:07:03.310
Okay.

1231
01:07:03.519 --> 01:07:07.182
I can see that. And why are
you pointing the gun at Frankie?

1232
01:07:07.256 --> 01:07:11.022
Because this bastard
ruined my whole life.

1233
01:07:11.260 --> 01:07:13.728
And now. I'm going to
shoot him. too!

1234
01:07:13.796 --> 01:07:15.286
Okay. Okay. Well...

1235
01:07:15.364 --> 01:07:19.061
You could do that. But let's...
Let's just think this through.

1236
01:07:19.135 --> 01:07:21.228
If you kill Frankie. I'm
going to have to kill you.

1237
01:07:21.303 --> 01:07:23.430
I don't want to.
but I will.

1238
01:07:23.572 --> 01:07:24.766
Is that what you want?

1239
01:07:24.840 --> 01:07:26.364
I don't care.

1240
01:07:27.043 --> 01:07:29.477
I have nothing to
live for anymore.

1241
01:07:30.079 --> 01:07:31.512
Sure you do.

1242
01:07:33.416 --> 01:07:36.715
I know. I know things seem
pretty bleak right now.

1243
01:07:36.786 --> 01:07:38.219
Okay. look.

1244
01:07:38.954 --> 01:07:40.319
Here's the thing.

1245
01:07:40.389 --> 01:07:42.949
Men lie. They cheat.
They start wars.

1246
01:07:43.025 --> 01:07:44.322
They're slobs
unless they're gay

1247
01:07:44.393 --> 01:07:45.724
and there's precious few
of them walking the planet

1248
01:07:45.795 --> 01:07:48.286
worth putting on lipstick for.
let alone throwing your life away.

1249
01:07:48.364 --> 01:07:49.388
Which is what
you'll be doing

1250
01:07:49.465 --> 01:07:52.093
if you shoot your festering
crap-bag of a husband.

1251
01:07:52.168 --> 01:07:53.226
Is that really necessary?

1252
01:07:53.302 --> 01:07:55.293
Shut up
or I'll shoot you.

1253
01:07:55.604 --> 01:07:57.834
I can't live
with him anymore.

1254
01:07:58.107 --> 01:08:01.304
Then. don't.
You don't have to. okay.

1255
01:08:04.046 --> 01:08:06.674
Felicia. as hard as
it is to imagine.

1256
01:08:06.749 --> 01:08:07.773
you have days
ahead of you

1257
01:08:07.850 --> 01:08:12.082
where you will smile and laugh
and look forward to things.

1258
01:08:12.154 --> 01:08:14.714
Maybe even
fall in love again.

1259
01:08:15.591 --> 01:08:17.024
If you don't
throw it all away.

1260
01:08:19.195 --> 01:08:20.560
I promise.

1261
01:08:21.464 --> 01:08:23.125
Oh. God.

1262
01:08:32.875 --> 01:08:36.140
Cathy's going to be
really pissed at me.

1263
01:08:59.502 --> 01:09:01.697
I'll catch up
with you later.

1264
01:09:04.874 --> 01:09:07.274
So. what's going to
happen to her?

1265
01:09:08.477 --> 01:09:10.206
Well. since she shot Mastro
in self-defense.

1266
01:09:10.279 --> 01:09:12.338
she'll probably get
a new identity

1267
01:09:12.414 --> 01:09:15.212
and be moved someplace
you can't find her.

1268
01:09:16.051 --> 01:09:18.383
He said he killed
little Frankie.

1269
01:09:18.721 --> 01:09:19.949
Do you believe him?

1270
01:09:20.022 --> 01:09:22.616
He's a lying scumbag.
There's no way.

1271
01:09:27.029 --> 01:09:29.122
You know.
it's a hell of a thing.

1272
01:09:29.198 --> 01:09:32.361
losing your wife and your
son all in the same day.

1273
01:09:32.635 --> 01:09:34.899
Do you ever think about
all the people. the families

1274
01:09:34.970 --> 01:09:37.370
had days like this
because of you?

1275
01:09:39.275 --> 01:09:41.368
The clock's still ticking.

1276
01:09:41.644 --> 01:09:43.111
Either you get me a name
by this time tomorrow...

1277
01:09:43.179 --> 01:09:44.737
Actually. Frankie.
name or no name.

1278
01:09:44.813 --> 01:09:46.007
this time tomorrow.
you're on your way

1279
01:09:46.081 --> 01:09:47.776
to a new city
and out of my hair.

1280
01:09:47.850 --> 01:09:51.286
I'm sorry for your loss.
but screw you and your clock.

1281
01:10:08.137 --> 01:10:11.072
I just want to wash the stench
of this day off and go to bed.

1282
01:10:11.140 --> 01:10:14.576
I know. But there are about 60 people
in there. hiding behind furniture.

1283
01:10:14.643 --> 01:10:15.905
just waiting for you
to open the door

1284
01:10:15.978 --> 01:10:18.640
so they can jump up
and yell. "Surprise. "

1285
01:10:18.714 --> 01:10:19.772
Yuck.

1286
01:10:19.848 --> 01:10:22.578
Come on. It's your birthday.
This isn't about you.

1287
01:10:22.651 --> 01:10:24.983
Now. get ready to
act surprised.

1288
01:10:25.888 --> 01:10:27.219
All right. all right.

1289
01:10:27.289 --> 01:10:28.813
That's my girl.

1290
01:10:37.866 --> 01:10:39.424
This is a surprise.

1291
01:10:40.903 --> 01:10:42.427
Huh.

1292
01:10:44.039 --> 01:10:46.564
Well. come on.
I'll buy you a drink.

1293
01:10:46.976 --> 01:10:49.206
Okay. But I'm
not putting out.

1294
01:11:00.289 --> 01:11:02.780
I have no idea
who these people are.

1295
01:11:03.559 --> 01:11:05.083
Ed. Jeannie.

1296
01:11:11.467 --> 01:11:12.525
Surprise!

1297
01:11:13.936 --> 01:11:16.336
She's my beautiful
birthday girl.

1298
01:11:16.405 --> 01:11:17.429
Okay.

1299
01:11:17.506 --> 01:11:19.167
Oh. happy birthday.
sweet pea.

1300
01:11:19.241 --> 01:11:20.708
Thanks. Ma.
Oh. you're welcome...

1301
01:11:20.776 --> 01:11:21.834
Okay.

1302
01:11:23.012 --> 01:11:25.344
How did you
keep this a secret?

1303
01:11:27.716 --> 01:11:28.842
You knew that I knew.

1304
01:11:28.917 --> 01:11:30.384
I knew that you knew.

1305
01:11:30.452 --> 01:11:32.386
Well. at least
that was a surprise.

1306
01:11:32.454 --> 01:11:34.513
I knew it would be.

1307
01:11:34.590 --> 01:11:37.889
Here. Mary. It's a
little... Little something.

1308
01:11:37.960 --> 01:11:38.949
Oh. Stan.

1309
01:11:39.028 --> 01:11:41.019
I know. Go ahead.
Open it. Open it.

1310
01:11:41.096 --> 01:11:42.222
Okay.

1311
01:11:43.932 --> 01:11:44.921
It's...

1312
01:11:46.568 --> 01:11:47.557
A fifty.

1313
01:11:47.870 --> 01:11:49.599
You gave her money?

1314
01:11:51.707 --> 01:11:52.696
You like it?

1315
01:11:53.075 --> 01:11:56.135
It... It's just what I
always wanted. Thank you.

1316
01:11:57.613 --> 01:11:58.739
See?
Thank you.

1317
01:11:58.847 --> 01:12:00.212
Yeah?

1318
01:12:00.316 --> 01:12:02.375
Is... Is Raph here?

1319
01:12:03.986 --> 01:12:05.476
No. I'm sorry.

1320
01:12:05.554 --> 01:12:07.545
It's okay.
I told him not to.

1321
01:12:07.623 --> 01:12:09.284
What about Brandi?

1322
01:12:12.761 --> 01:12:16.253
She thinks you don't
want her at your party.

1323
01:12:16.732 --> 01:12:18.825
I see.

1324
01:12:22.705 --> 01:12:24.297
You're going to keep looking
at me with those sad eyes

1325
01:12:24.373 --> 01:12:26.841
until I go talk
to her. aren't you?

1326
01:12:30.279 --> 01:12:32.076
I know you mean well.

1327
01:12:33.082 --> 01:12:35.516
But you're not
a very good mother.

1328
01:12:37.886 --> 01:12:40.377
You're right next to her.
I get it.

1329
01:12:42.358 --> 01:12:45.293
I can't believe
you gave her cash.

1330
01:12:45.994 --> 01:12:48.121
Huh? I know.

1331
01:12:50.199 --> 01:12:52.099
Good party. huh?

1332
01:12:57.172 --> 01:12:59.800
Hey. Squish.
What's going on?

1333
01:13:01.410 --> 01:13:02.638
Nothing.

1334
01:13:04.947 --> 01:13:06.039
You okay?

1335
01:13:06.115 --> 01:13:07.207
Yeah.

1336
01:13:10.686 --> 01:13:11.710
No.

1337
01:13:13.555 --> 01:13:14.783
Listen.

1338
01:13:16.258 --> 01:13:18.055
Can you do
something for me?

1339
01:13:18.127 --> 01:13:19.151
What?

1340
01:13:19.228 --> 01:13:23.562
It's just... I've... I've spent
my whole day watching people cry.

1341
01:13:23.632 --> 01:13:25.361
Making people cry.

1342
01:13:25.801 --> 01:13:27.359
Wanting to cry.

1343
01:13:28.637 --> 01:13:29.934
Anyway...

1344
01:13:30.072 --> 01:13:33.064
I know it would make me
feel a whole lot better

1345
01:13:33.142 --> 01:13:37.636
if for my birthday maybe you
could just hold off on crying.

1346
01:13:38.247 --> 01:13:41.273
Just until tomorrow.
Could you do that for me?

1347
01:13:41.517 --> 01:13:42.609
Yeah.

1348
01:13:46.455 --> 01:13:48.047
Okay. Come here.

1349
01:13:48.524 --> 01:13:49.923
It's okay.

1350
01:13:50.626 --> 01:13:52.958
Come on. Come on.

1351
01:13:54.229 --> 01:13:55.423
Whatever it is.
we'll make it better.

1352
01:13:57.399 --> 01:14:00.630
I'm so sorry I make
your life so miserable.

1353
01:14:00.769 --> 01:14:03.795
Oh. God. Listen to me. Listen to me.

1354
01:14:04.206 --> 01:14:06.766
You don't make
my life miserable. Okay?

1355
01:14:07.009 --> 01:14:09.534
I just...
I get frustrated sometimes.

1356
01:14:10.078 --> 01:14:12.410
You know.
I want you to be happy.

1357
01:14:12.781 --> 01:14:16.012
And I want you to stop doing
stuff that hurts yourself.

1358
01:14:16.084 --> 01:14:18.644
That makes you miserable.
That's all.

1359
01:14:19.788 --> 01:14:20.880
Come on.

1360
01:14:22.257 --> 01:14:23.281
Okay.

1361
01:14:23.358 --> 01:14:25.918
Stop. Stop.

1362
01:14:26.161 --> 01:14:27.423
Come on.

1363
01:14:30.532 --> 01:14:32.591
There's my pretty
baby sister.

1364
01:14:37.439 --> 01:14:40.067
I got you something
for your birthday.

1365
01:14:41.410 --> 01:14:42.399
Really?

1366
01:14:42.478 --> 01:14:43.604
Yeah.

1367
01:14:45.080 --> 01:14:46.342
You didn't have to.

1368
01:14:46.415 --> 01:14:48.610
I know. I know.
I just wanted to.

1369
01:14:59.161 --> 01:15:00.355
Wow.

1370
01:15:00.429 --> 01:15:02.454
It's an Indian talisman.

1371
01:15:03.265 --> 01:15:04.527
Or totem.

1372
01:15:05.267 --> 01:15:08.259
Maybe. I don't...
I forget which. but...

1373
01:15:09.771 --> 01:15:12.797
I got it from this Indian stand
after I took off with Chico's car.

1374
01:15:12.875 --> 01:15:14.137
Raphael.

1375
01:15:14.710 --> 01:15:15.904
Right.

1376
01:15:15.978 --> 01:15:18.173
It's from
the Los Lobos Tribe.

1377
01:15:18.247 --> 01:15:19.509
Sweetie.

1378
01:15:20.549 --> 01:15:22.312
Los Lobos is a band.

1379
01:15:22.951 --> 01:15:24.179
A band of Indians?

1380
01:15:24.253 --> 01:15:25.948
No. Just a band.

1381
01:15:26.755 --> 01:15:29.553
Oh. Well. anyway.
it means.

1382
01:15:29.625 --> 01:15:31.286
"May you always sleep
under the tall trees. "

1383
01:15:31.360 --> 01:15:34.693
So. that's nice. right?

1384
01:15:41.470 --> 01:15:43.233
That's really nice.

1385
01:15:43.338 --> 01:15:44.930
So. you like it?

1386
01:15:46.508 --> 01:15:49.534
I like it.
I like it a lot.

1387
01:15:50.879 --> 01:15:52.676
Thank you.
Thank you so much.

1388
01:15:55.083 --> 01:15:56.812
Listen. I have to
go do something.

1389
01:15:56.885 --> 01:15:59.786
But when I come back
I want to talk. Okay?

1390
01:15:59.855 --> 01:16:01.015
Okay.

1391
01:16:01.356 --> 01:16:02.482
Okay.

1392
01:16:39.528 --> 01:16:41.894
Come on.
We've got work to do.

1393
01:16:41.964 --> 01:16:44.524
Oh. Can't it wait
until tomorrow?

1394
01:16:44.600 --> 01:16:46.568
Move your ass. Marshall.

1395
01:16:48.837 --> 01:16:50.634
What?
What?

1396
01:16:51.239 --> 01:16:52.228
What's that about?

1397
01:16:52.307 --> 01:16:54.002
I don't know.
They don't tell me anything.

1398
01:16:54.076 --> 01:16:55.805
Huh? They don't tell me anything.

1399
01:16:55.877 --> 01:16:57.538
But you're the boss.
They have to tell you.

1400
01:16:57.613 --> 01:16:58.637
I know.

1401
01:16:58.714 --> 01:16:59.942
I mean. you should know.

1402
01:17:17.165 --> 01:17:18.393
Let's set it up
right here.

1403
01:17:18.467 --> 01:17:20.196
Let's go. Paul. Joe. with me.

1404
01:17:26.141 --> 01:17:27.506
Okay. Here's how I think
we should proceed.

1405
01:17:28.310 --> 01:17:29.504
Open up. Talltrees!

1406
01:17:29.578 --> 01:17:31.239
I think I'll just stand
here with my thumb up my ass

1407
01:17:31.313 --> 01:17:32.940
while you start shouting
like a crazy person.

1408
01:17:33.448 --> 01:17:35.916
After a while.
it becomes charming.

1409
01:17:36.518 --> 01:17:38.145
What is all this?

1410
01:17:38.520 --> 01:17:39.612
What happened?

1411
01:17:39.688 --> 01:17:42.282
Did Sienna get tired of
sleeping under the tall trees?

1412
01:17:42.357 --> 01:17:45.292
You think I was having
an affair with Sienna?

1413
01:17:45.360 --> 01:17:48.193
Not only is that disgusting.
It's slander.

1414
01:17:48.830 --> 01:17:50.855
And you had better be very
careful with your accusations.

1415
01:17:50.932 --> 01:17:52.866
Excuse me.
Do you mind?

1416
01:17:54.102 --> 01:17:55.160
Go ahead.

1417
01:17:55.237 --> 01:17:56.829
Edwin Talltrees.

1418
01:17:57.039 --> 01:17:59.803
I have a warrant to search this
property for any and all evidence

1419
01:17:59.875 --> 01:18:03.470
relating to the murder of Francis
Amato Junior and Sienna Burke.

1420
01:18:03.545 --> 01:18:05.376
Please step outside.

1421
01:18:18.160 --> 01:18:19.320
Wait.

1422
01:18:22.330 --> 01:18:23.763
What?

1423
01:18:24.166 --> 01:18:25.428
Look.

1424
01:18:26.068 --> 01:18:28.628
At what? Oh.

1425
01:18:38.714 --> 01:18:40.511
Stop right there.

1426
01:18:40.782 --> 01:18:42.249
Don't come any closer
or I swear I'll...

1427
01:18:42.317 --> 01:18:45.252
What?
Kick the stool out?

1428
01:18:50.959 --> 01:18:53.154
Please. Let me.

1429
01:18:53.762 --> 01:18:55.662
Hey. what are
you doing?

1430
01:18:59.701 --> 01:19:02.693
<i>So. after spending almost
their entire lives together.</i>

1431
01:19:02.771 --> 01:19:04.136
<i>Sienna Burke
broke up with Kyle</i>

1432
01:19:04.206 --> 01:19:07.471
<i>because she couldn't tell her
friends she was with an Indian.</i>

1433
01:19:07.542 --> 01:19:10.238
<i>She broke his heart.
so he cut out hers.</i>

1434
01:19:11.012 --> 01:19:12.809
<i>That almost seems fair.</i>

1435
01:19:17.886 --> 01:19:19.683
Thanks for the call.

1436
01:19:19.921 --> 01:19:21.479
It's your case.

1437
01:19:21.623 --> 01:19:22.954
The U.S. Marshals have
a long history

1438
01:19:23.024 --> 01:19:25.424
of cooperating with
local law enforcement.

1439
01:19:25.494 --> 01:19:26.722
Uh-huh.

1440
01:19:26.928 --> 01:19:29.624
After all I've done
to get us off the reservation.

1441
01:19:29.698 --> 01:19:32.531
to give my son the same
opportunities as the whites.

1442
01:19:32.601 --> 01:19:34.466
they still treat him
like a redskin.

1443
01:19:34.536 --> 01:19:35.594
But he won't be
tried like one.

1444
01:19:35.670 --> 01:19:36.728
Whatever.

1445
01:19:36.805 --> 01:19:39.399
I've got white man's money.
A white man's lawyer.

1446
01:19:39.474 --> 01:19:43.001
And I promise you. my son won't
spend a day in prison.

1447
01:19:43.678 --> 01:19:45.805
Hey. Chuckles.

1448
01:19:46.414 --> 01:19:49.508
Your son's a monster. He gutted
Sienna Burke while she was still alive

1449
01:19:49.584 --> 01:19:51.313
and he needs to be
put down.

1450
01:19:51.386 --> 01:19:53.786
But guess what. He's not the
only monster on the block.

1451
01:19:53.855 --> 01:19:56.915
Not by a long shot.
And prison or no prison.

1452
01:19:56.992 --> 01:20:00.325
tomorrow morning. the very worst
of those monsters is coming for him.

1453
01:20:00.395 --> 01:20:02.886
So. good luck with
your white man's defense.

1454
01:20:02.964 --> 01:20:05.592
Let me know how
that works out for you.

1455
01:20:06.568 --> 01:20:07.660
Oh.

1456
01:20:07.969 --> 01:20:12.303
And you might want to think about
adding a little security for yourself.

1457
01:20:14.709 --> 01:20:17.974
Hey. hey. hey.
Is she seeing anyone?

1458
01:21:00.856 --> 01:21:02.153
Oh. crud.

1459
01:21:09.030 --> 01:21:10.930
Hi. You're awake.

1460
01:21:11.566 --> 01:21:12.624
Duh.

1461
01:21:12.701 --> 01:21:15.169
I didn't want to
miss my groceries.

1462
01:21:15.303 --> 01:21:17.134
Sorry. I got hung up.

1463
01:21:17.606 --> 01:21:18.766
Is this what you mean
when you say.

1464
01:21:18.840 --> 01:21:21.104
"I be back
a little later"?

1465
01:21:21.176 --> 01:21:23.201
I wish to know.
For future.

1466
01:21:23.511 --> 01:21:25.069
No. I'm usually very prompt.

1467
01:21:25.146 --> 01:21:28.013
I... Something happened.

1468
01:21:29.317 --> 01:21:30.648
More dead people?

1469
01:21:30.719 --> 01:21:31.811
No.

1470
01:21:32.721 --> 01:21:34.382
Well. yes. but...

1471
01:21:35.557 --> 01:21:37.684
Tasha. I meant what I said.

1472
01:21:37.759 --> 01:21:40.193
As long as you follow
the rules of the program.

